snippet.title: The Voidness - Official Gameplay Announcement Trailer 2023 (Horror Lidar Game)
snippet.description:

Official gameplay trailer for The Voidness, a psychological horror game I have been working on where you have to scan the environment to see. Try and escape The Voidness, but you are not alone...
